author: slanidrac16
title: I'm over it...look at next week!
text: Posts: 5,841 I'm over it...look at next week! It still stings a little but c'mon deep in your heart did you think we were not going to lose a game this year? I know, I know, division game , in our house, yadda, yadda, yadda. Let's get er done next week and , OH LOOK, the Seahawks are traveling to Cincy and the Rams are going to Green Bay. We need to take care of business and in a couple of weeks last Sunday will be a faint memory...until we go to St. Louis! We've got a pretty damn good team here and any loss can and will be analyzed and scrutinized BECAUSE we are a good team. But let's take a deep breath and enjoy this season. It STILL has special written all over it!
